#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Between 2021 and 2023 Tails, [Tor](https://torproject.org/), and the "
"[Guardian Project](https://guardianproject.info/) partnered to organize "
"training and usability tests in Ecuador, Mexico, and Brazil. Our goals were "
"to:"
msgstr ""
"Entre 2021 y 2023 Tails, [Tor](https://torproject.org/), y [Guardian Project]"
"(https://guardianproject.info/) se asociaron para organizar capacitaciones y "
"pruebas de usabilidad en Ecuador, México y Brasil. Nuestros objetivos eran:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Promote our digital security tools and train human rights defenders in the "
"Global South."
msgstr ""
"Promocionar nuestras herramientas de seguridad digital y capacitar a "
"defensores de derechos humanos en el Sur Global."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"- Learn from their experiences and needs to help us prioritize future work."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Improve the usability of our tools based on their feedback."
msgstr ""

