#, no-wrap
msgid "Trainings"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Through our combined efforts we reached 47 organizations and trained 433 "
"human rights defenders on our family of tools based on the Tor network. For "
"Tails only, we conducted 8 workshops and trained 84 people on using Tails: "
"journalists, activists, feminists, lawyers, and human rights defenders."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The material used for these Tails workshops is available on our website in "
"[English](https://tails.net/contribute/how/promote/slides/"
"Ciclo_Autodefensa_Digital_202204/Tails-English.odp), [Spanish](https://tails."
"net/contribute/how/promote/slides/Ciclo_Autodefensa_Digital_202204/Tails-"
"Spanish.odp), and [Portuguese](https://tails.net/contribute/how/promote/"
"slides/Ciclo_Autodefensa_Digital_202204/Tails-Portuguese.odp)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Assistants to the workshops were able to start Tails on all their PC "
"computers but had more frequent issues with Mac computers."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"From what is already possible to do with Tails, people were most interested "
"in using Tails to:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Handle sensitive data, for example, medical data of abortion patients, "
"sensitive documents from political trials, or field studies from human "
"rights violations. That said, not all journalists thought that they were "
"manipulating data that was sensitive enough to require a tool like Tails.  "
"Sometimes it was hard to draw the line on when to use Tails and when not."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Investigate sensitive topics online, either for journalistic purposes, "
"medical purposes, or when making safe travel plans."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Have a secure OS when using other people's computer, either when traveling "
"or when people don't have the means to have their own computer."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"From what is not possible yet to do with Tails, people were most interested "
"in:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Doing online meetings and using mobile messaging apps like Signal and "
"Telegram from Tails."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "- Using a VPN instead of Tor for speed and access to more websites."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We included both of these objectives in our 3-year product strategy.  You "
"can track our progress in the GitLab issues related to [[!tails_ticket "
"19472]]."
msgstr ""
"Incluimos ambos objetivos en nuestra estrategia de producto a 3 años. Puedes "
"seguir nuestro progreso en los problemas de GitLab relacionados con [[!"
"tails_ticket 19472]]."
